OL,3,CMan who killed 71-year-old neighbour
OL,4,Cwith kitchen knife jailed
OL,6,FA man who attacked and killed his 71-
OL,7,Fyear-old neighbour has been sentenced
OL,8,Fto life at Swansea Crown Court for
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FBrian Whitelock, 57, attacked Wendy
OL,12,FBuckney with a kitchen knife, a broken
OL,13,Ftable leg and wooden shelving during a
OL,14,Fsustained assault in her own home.
OL,16,FThe pensioner was discovered, naked
OL,17,Fand covered in blood, in the living
OL,18,Froom of her home in Clydach, near
OL,19,FSwansea, on August 23 2022.
