OL,6,FThe court previously heard how
OL,7,FWhitelock had also been jailed for
OL,8,Flife in 2001 for murder and
OL,9,Fmanslaughter but was released from
OL,10,Fprison in 2018.
OL,12,FWhitelock will now spend the rest of
OL,13,Fhis life behind bars as the judge said
OL,14,F"the seriousness" of the crime is so
OL,15,F"exceptionally high" that the
OL,16,Fpunishment should be a whole life
OL,17,Fprison order.
