OL,6,FThe defendant said: "What's the point?"
OL,8,FTrial judge Mr Justice Griffiths asked
OL,9,FWhitelock if he had any comments in
OL,10,Fresponse to the proposed whole life
OL,11,Forder.
OL,13,FWhitelock replied: "What can I say? I
OL,14,Fdidn't deserve it, head injury or not."
OL,16,FImposing a whole life order, the judge
OL,17,Fsaid Ms Buckney had given him money
OL,18,Ffor odd jobs and provided him with
OL,19,Ffood.
