OL,6,F"You described her as like a second
OL,7,Fmother to you. She deserved nothing
OL,8,Fbut your gratitude, but you brutally
OL,9,Fmurdered her, and you have never, ever
OL,10,Fsuggested a motive," he said.
OL,12,F"You killed her for your own pleasure.
OL,13,FAfter the cruelty of your attack on
OL,14,Fher in life, you degraded her body in
OL,15,Fdeath.
OL,17,F"You yourself told people afterwards
OL,18,Fthat she was begging you to stop. You
OL,19,Fdescribed it as torture and that is
OL,20,Fwhat it was.
