OL,6,F"There is no doubt that there was a
OL,7,Fsexual element to the pleasure you
OL,8,Ftook in your attack."
OL,10,FThe judge added: "This a case of the
OL,11,Fmost extreme gravity.
OL,13,F"I have no doubt that the seriousness
OL,14,Fof this murder is so exceptionally
OL,15,Fhigh that just punishment requires you
OL,16,Fto be kept in prison for the rest of
OL,17,Fyour life.
OL,19,F"Therefore, the early release
OL,20,Fprovisions will not apply and you will
OL,21,Fnever be considered for parole."
