OL,6,FDuring the trial, Christopher Rees KC,
OL,7,Fprosecuting, said Whitelock had a long-
OL,8,Fstanding drug addiction and history of
OL,9,Fviolence.
OL,11,FMr Rees said Ms Buckney must have
OL,12,F"suffered greatly" at the hands of
OL,13,FWhitelock before her death, having
OL,14,Fsustained multiple stab injuries,
OL,15,Fsharp force injuries and blunt force
OL,16,Finjuries.
