OL,6,FWhitelock had previously been jailed
OL,7,Fin 2001 after he battered Nicholas
OL,8,FMorgan to death with an axe handle and
OL,9,Fset fire to his body. Whitelock's
OL,10,Fbrother, Glen, who was asleep, died in
OL,11,Fthe subsequent blaze.
OL,13,FHe was released from prison in 2018
OL,14,Fand moved in opposite Ms Buckney, who
OL,15,Femployed him to do odd jobs, including
OL,16,Fgardening.
