OL,6,FAnother neighbour, Paul Jones, heard
OL,7,FWhitelock say, "I didn't realise what
OL,8,FI was doing until I came down from the
OL,9,Fhigh".
OL,11,FThe jury also heard Whitelock had
OL,12,Fpreviously told doctors he took "30
OL,13,FPolish diazepam a day" bought off the
OL,14,Fstreet.
OL,16,FA doctor who carried out a CT scan
OL,17,Fahead of the incident believed
OL,18,FWhitelock's confusion in the weeks
OL,19,Fbefore was caused by drug withdrawal,
OL,20,Frather than his head injury.
