OL,6,FIn a statement released following the
OL,7,Fjury's guilty verdict, Ms Buckney's
OL,8,Ffamily described her as a "much loved
OL,9,Fsister and aunty".
OL,11,FThey said: "Today's verdict brings
OL,12,Fsome measure of justice for Wendy, who
OL,13,Fwas taken from us far too soon.
OL,15,F"While nothing can bring her back, we
OL,16,Fare grateful that the truth has been
OL,17,Fheard.
OL,19,F"Wendy was a very much loved sister
OL,20,Fand aunty whose kindness, laughter and
OL,21,Fspirit touched the lives of so many.
