OL,6,F"Our lives will never be the same
OL,7,Fwithout her, but we will continue to
OL,8,Fhonour her memory every day.
OL,10,F"This has been a painful and
OL,11,Fheartbreaking journey for our family.
OL,13,F"We thank everyone who has supported
OL,14,Fus during this incredibly difficult
OL,15,Ftime and we ask for privacy as we
OL,16,Fcontinue to grieve and heal in the
OL,17,Fwake of this tragedy."
